

 Q1. What are the limitations of EntityManager methods to perform CRUD operations with DB?
 
 Answer)   
			
			1. Persist :- Retrieving Entity obj based on only ID field(PK field) @Id
			
			2. Find  :- Multiple Entity obj retrival is not possible (multiple record)
			
			3. Remove :- Bulk update and bulk delete is also not possible
			
			4. Merge :- To access Entity obj we can not specify some extra condition.